  "body": "<h2>Reimagined GUI</h2>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/yKr2SDOD/images/cc18efcefad38b64f57d3eafc54238f65250a054.png\"><br>\n<p><b>!If you're looking for original Dark version, here it is <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/reimaginedguidark\">Reimagined GUI (Dark)</a></b></p>\n<p><b>!If you're looking for light version, here it is <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/reimaginedguilight\">Reimagined GUI (Light)</a></b></p>\n<p>Replaces every container in the game, changes hotbar, hearts and armor icons.</p>\n<p>For a better experience I recommend using <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/raised\">Raised</a> mod(It fixes the code that cuts off the selector texture by two pixels on the bottom.)</p>\n<div>\n<p>You can support me and my projects here:</p>\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/AmongstReality\"><img src=\"https://github.com/AmongstReality/SomeImages/blob/main/patreon.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Patreon\"></a>\n</div><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/yKr2SDOD/images/1915b6a069d7c97383f6d71d6ba713df02600494.png\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/yKr2SDOD/images/0d280e56dcfa5822ccc1d0ba5abf56617aefd76c.png\">\n\n<h3>Supprted Mods:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/backslot\">Backslot</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/capes\">Capes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/inventorio\">Inventorio</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/midnightcontrols\">MidnightControls</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/modmenu\">ModMenu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/no-chat-reports\">No Chat Reports</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/notebook\">Vanilla Notebook</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/shulkerboxtooltip\">ShulkerBoxTooltip</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/metal-barrels/files\">Metal Barrels</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Additional Links:</h3